        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites </strong>@Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.Ikqay8buYlb85bwd]{Counterspell}</p>\n<hr>\n<p>When you successfully use Counterspell to counteract a spell that affects targeted creatures or an area, you can turn that spell’s effect back on its caster.</p>\n<p>When reflected, the spell affects only the original caster, even if it’s an area spell or it would normally affect more than one creature. The original caster can attempt a save and use other defenses against the reflected spell as normal.</p>",
